    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "`CaptureStart` is only called at the beginning of the transaction. The `create` flag indicates if its a create transaction (i.e. `tx.to` is empty) or not. I don't think create transactions can generate `CREATE2`-style addresses.\r\n\r\nYou should instead use `CaptureEnter` which is for every call frame (except topmost one). It has a `typ` parameter which you can check like `typ == vm.CREATE2`.",
